I see what your saying with watching something from a different culture and it still being fulfilling. Research can help you understand something or bring you closer to understanding but sometimes you don't really understand something until you're immersed in it. I was thinking, yeah I might realize what the "lost decade" is but I haven't actually experienced it. That's going to influence how I interpret it.<br />
